Type: Package
Package: richCluster
Title: Fast, Robust Clustering Algorithms for Gene Enrichment Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-09-20
Authors@R: c(
    person("Junguk", "Hur", , "junguk.hur@med.und.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Sarah", "Hong", , "ssh2198@columbia.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Jane", "Kim", , "j6kim2026@chadwickschool.org", role = "aut")
  )
Description: The richCluster package contains a fast C++ agglomerative
    hierarchical clustering algorithm packaged into easily callable R
    functions, designed to help cluster biological 'terms' based on how
    similar of genes are expressed in their activation.
